<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">Client Care FAQ</h2>

  <div class="faq-accordion">
    <!-- Question 1 -->
    <div class="accordion-item active">
      <div class="accordion-header" role="button" aria-expanded="true">
        How do I determine my correct size at Thistlewood?
        <span>&plus;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-content" style="display: block;">
        Our garments are drafted following heritage British lines, which often favor relaxed, fluid drapes or structured architectural cuts. Each product page lists specific fit tips. For standard body sizes, select your typical sizing. S is cut for EU 36/38, M for EU 38/40, L for EU 42, and XL for EU 44. Feel free to contact our studio for custom measurement reviews.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Question 2 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <div class="accordion-header" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
        Where are your clothes fabricated?
        <span>&plus;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        Every single piece in our collections is patterned, cut, and sewn in our private design studio located at 12 Savile Row in London, United Kingdom. We do not license production to secondary assembly plants; everything is crafted directly under the oversight of our creative director.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Question 3 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <div class="accordion-header" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
        What is your shipping and delivery protocol?
        <span>&plus;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        We provide complimentary premium express shipping on all orders. Each item is steamed, wrapped in custom tissue, and placed within a signature breathable organic linen garment cover with cedar blocks. Courier shipments are dispatched via tracked DHL Express or FedEx Priority.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Question 4 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <div class="accordion-header" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
        What is the return policy for luxury archive purchases?
        <span>&plus;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        We accept return inquiries for garments in perfect, unworn condition with security tags attached within 14 days of delivery. Returns are eligible for size exchanges or store credit. Return shipping charges are complementary. Please email inquiries@thistlewood.com to initiate a return shipping label.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Question 5 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <div class="accordion-header" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
        Do you accept custom alterations or bespoke sizing?
        <span>&plus;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        Yes. If you fall outside our S/M/L/XL sizing boundaries or require specific adjustments (sleeve length adjustments, hemline alterations, custom fabric swaps), select the 'Bespoke Custom Fabric Selection' category in our contact form or visit our London studio. Bespoke items carry an additional tailoring surcharge.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
